{
  "stem": "13395.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the jar broke.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the jam was all over the door and the floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I thought it was funny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But this was, this was the life in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, all the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There would-- a Jew would-- I remember the men would wear their coats with their collars up and would hide their beards so they-- and pull down their hats.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would run for prayers because you couldn't stop the Jews from praying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, the religious life went on, even, even with the Nazis being there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would see somebody running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would grab him by his beard, cut it off, and, you know, ridicule him and, and kick him and beat him in the street.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you always hear, heard this thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the neighboring town, they hung four Jews for just leaving the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was all, all the time things happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But, as I said, you tried to stay in your place, in your room, go out as little as possible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then those awful rumors that were circulating-- most of what we survived on was on rumors of hope, that the war is ending and that the Nazis are being defeated.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was nothing to it, but I guess we needed this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm trying to think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember it right now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- because I was a stranger in that area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was later in camp with some girls from there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we only knew my paternal grandmother came with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kaufman, Ida Kaufman and [NON-ENGLISH] Kaufman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, she was Steinitz before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came with us to Jaworzno.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my maternal grandmother was shipped, because she lived in another town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was shipped to a town in Poland called Olkusz.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
